      <title>卡塔尔在最新的阿萨德后提升中向叙利亚提供叙利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/qatar-supplies-syria-with-natural-gas-in-latest-post-assad-boost</link>
